column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, pz.z as phz , pz.zErr as phzErr, s.z, e.lgm_tot_p5#, e.lgm_tot_p8#, e.lgm_tot_p1#, e.sfr_tot_p5#, e.sfr_tot_p8#, e.sfr_tot_p1#, z.spiral, z.elliptical, e.bptclass, g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err, g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err, g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err, g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux_err, g.sii_#_flux, g.sii_#_flux_err, g.sii_#_flux, g.sii_#_flux_err, g.h_alpha_reqw, g.h_alpha_reqw_err, g.oiii_#_reqw, g.oiii_#_reqw_err, p.petroMag_u, p.petroMag_g, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_i, p.petroMag_z, p.petroMagErr_u, p.petroMagErr_g, p.petroMagErr_r, p.petroMagErr_i, p.petroMagErr_z, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z from PhotoObjAll AS p LEFT JOIN Photoz AS pz ON pz.objID = p.objID LEFT JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS sp ON sp.objID = p.objID LEFT JOIN galSpecLine AS g ON g.specobjid = sp.specobjid LEFT JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = sp.specobjid LEFT JOIN zooSpec as z on z.specobjid = sp.specobjid LEFT JOIN galSpecExtra AS e ON e.specobjid = sp.specobjid WHERE type = # AND p.petroMagErr_u > # AND p.petroMagErr_g > # AND p.petroMagErr_r > # AND p.petroMagErr_i > # AND p.petroMagErr_z > # AND pz.zErr > # AND pz.photoErrorClass> #
